title: Laura Ingraham Aug 25 Podcast.mp3
description:
Laura Ingraham august 25, 2016 mp3 Podcast

Byron York - Chief political correspondent for the Washington Examiner, Fox News contributor, and syndicated columnist. On Trump immigration policy "I can't remember him talking about deportation, he always talks about the wall." Dr. Sebastian Gorka - Author of Defeating Jihad and Chair of Military Theory at the Marine Corps University. On Iran "They're laughing in our face, this is what happens when you lead from behind" Gerard Robinson - Resident fellow at the American Enterprise Institute, specializing in education policy studies "All Americans are interested in having a quality education for their children."
